{"tid":697914,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE過來人又想幫返DSE嘅入一入來","createTime":"2018-06-11T09:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T15:25:17.000Z","uid":46047,"like":9,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b4a4e68d5266e77b17cd64a17addbb0dadfb0f0c","tid":697914,"uid":46047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T09:26:54.000Z","msg":"來緊7月11號就係放榜<br />\n唔知大家仲記唔記得放榜當時好迷惘好需要人意見嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地每年都會喺網上面解答大家升學嘅疑難<br />\n如果想幫手或者知多啲都可以填一填份google form<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/8Xr0dNJi4epPUiFm1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2F8Xr0dNJi4epPUiFm1&d=YagISGyFobxopJgWThF5%2Fv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=6bae6b50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/8Xr0dNJi4epPUiFm1</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"74d9660533ec41c53636a8cbd8dab8a6632093d5","tid":697914,"uid":46047,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T09:27:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/cXWFoyrZ3QbNwkry2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FcXWFoyrZ3QbNwkry2&d=YagISGyFobxopJgWThF5%2Fv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=cd5733d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/cXWFoyrZ3QbNwkry2</a><br />\n自膠呢條link先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91fcaa3f773b4abaa2ec1e53280ec9f8861d1062","tid":697914,"uid":19920,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T09:28:35.000Z","msg":"未放榜 講咩都無用啦"},{"pid":"a770aafc77e509c0a9f6038651d745340bdf4180","tid":697914,"uid":46047,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"91fcaa3f773b4abaa2ec1e53280ec9f8861d1062","tid":697914,"uid":19920,"lik